text: Tya striyanvara kasalahi gunha nahi tya apalya pityancya, apalya putrancya ani bhavancya, apalya putanyancya, bhacyancya ani apalya (paricita) striyancya ani jyancya tya malaka aheta tyam (dasa dasim) cya samora asavyata.1 Striyanno! Allahace bhaya balagata raha, allaha nihsansaya, pratyeka gostivara saksi ahe
